Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.68,1:03:06.11,EDZH1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\move(1320,70,1240,70,0,5500)\blur3}只因愛值得付出人生
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.91,1:03:08.62,EDZH1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\move(1240,70,1320,70,0,5500)\blur3}尊貴…真誠…
